    <item>
      <title>英国航空公司所有者超出预期，削减运力目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/british-airways-owner-beats-estimates-trims-2024-capacity-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际航空集团（IAG SA）公布第三季度收益超出预期，得益于跨大西洋航线需求增加，该公司表示，预计强劲的财务表现将持续到今年剩余时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/british-airways-owner-beats-estimates-trims-2024-capacity-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 07:42:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>食品配送平台 Swiggy 首次公开募股 (IPO) 最后一天售罄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/food-delivery-platform-swiggy-s-ipo-sold-out-on-final-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度食品外卖平台 Swiggy Ltd. 的 13 亿美元首次公开募股在竞标最后一天全部售罄，但由于大型投资者早期需求疲软，销售速度较慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/food-delivery-platform-swiggy-s-ipo-sold-out-on-final-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 07:27:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度在分析师投诉后提前公布 GDP 数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/india-moves-gdp-release-time-earlier-after-analyst-complaints</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于分析师表示没有足够的时间来分析数据，印度政府将国内生产总值和通胀数据的发布时间提前了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/india-moves-gdp-release-time-earlier-after-analyst-complaints</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 07:18:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国财政部将于下午 4 点就债务互换计划举行简报会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-s-finance-ministry-to-brief-at-4-p-m-on-debt-swap-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将于周五下午四点在北京就允许地方政府为其表外债务再融资的计划举行简报会，预计官员们将在会上公布更多旨在提振放缓经济的财政方案细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-s-finance-ministry-to-brief-at-4-p-m-on-debt-swap-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 06:41:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政策问题依然存在，投资者减少“特朗普交易”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/investors-dial-back-trump-trades-as-policy-doubts-seep-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在最初蜂拥进入“特朗普交易”之后，一些资产类别的投资者的热情正在逐渐消退，因为他们质疑唐纳德·特朗普作为美国总统是否会推行其雄心勃勃的关税提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/investors-dial-back-trump-trades-as-policy-doubts-seep-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 05:10:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将放宽海外资金获取 12 亿美元绿色债务的渠道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/india-moves-1-2-billion-of-green-debt-to-index-tracking-menu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度发行了 1000 亿卢比（12 亿美元）的绿色债券，可能被纳入摩根大通的旗舰新兴市场债务指数，这表明官员们正在寻求推动可持续的融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/india-moves-1-2-billion-of-green-debt-to-index-tracking-menu</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 02:48:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政计划悬而未决，中国股市下跌，周涨幅缩减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/chinese-stocks-head-for-weekly-gain-as-traders-await-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市下跌，反映出投资者在一场重要立法会议结束前的谨慎态度，投资者希望该会议能出台更有力的刺激措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/chinese-stocks-head-for-weekly-gain-as-traders-await-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 01:49:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场消化特朗普和中国影响 油价有望本周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价下跌，但仍有望实现周线上涨，因为市场正在消化特朗普第二任总统的影响，包括是否会刺激第一大进口国中国扩大刺激措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市因关注中国会议而缩减涨幅：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市回吐早前的涨幅，因投资者等待中国一场重要立法会议的结果，预计该会议将出台政策支持措施以提振疲软的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:14:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
